'''Marie-Clémence Andriamonta Paes''' (wavutse 1959), ni umukinnyi wa firime w’Abafaransa wo muri Malagasi<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0086972/</ref> .  Yakoze inyandiko nyinshi zamamaye cyane zirimo: ''Angano.'' ''.'' ''.'' ''Angano.'' ''.'' ''.'' , ''Mahaleo'' na ''L'opéra du bout du monde'' . Usibye gutanga icyerekezo, ni producer numwanditsi<ref>https://dafilms.com/director/10097-marie-clemence-paes</ref>. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1959 kuri se w’umufaransa na nyina wa Malagasy.  Yarangije impamyabumenyi ihanitse muri Sociology na Marketing CELSA-Sorbonne Diploma <ref>https://frenchculture.org/events/11052-fahavalo-madagascar-1947-director-marie-clemence-andriamonta-paes</ref>.Yashakanye na César Paes, akaba n'umuyobozi wa filimi uvuka muri Franco-Berezile<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes?no=7524</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1988, yatangije uruganda rwigenga rukorera i Paris rwitwa 'Laterit Productions' hamwe n'umugabo we César<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/marie-clemence-andriamonta-paes/</ref>.  Isosiyete ikora ibicuruzwa yiyemeje gukwirakwiza no gutangaza. Hamwe numugabo we César Paes, yanditse kandi akora documentaire nka ''Angano.'' ''.'' ''.'' ''Angano.'' ''.'' ''.'' ''Umugani wo muri Madagasikari'' , ''Indirimbo n'amarira ya Kamere'', na ''Soup ya Awara''<ref>http://www.film-documentaire.fr/4DACTION/w_liste_generique/C_36529_F</ref> . ''Awara Soup'' yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi muri Cinéma du Réel, Festival dei Popoli na Dok Leipzig . Filime ze nka ''Saudade do Futuro'', ''Mahaleo'', ''Opera yo mu nyanja y'Ubuhinde'' ''n'indirimbo za Madagasikari'' zasohotse mu ikinamico mu [[Bufaransa]] no muri [[Amerika]]<ref>https://tisch.nyu.edu/performance-studies/events/ay-2019-20/screening-of-fahavalo-with-filmmaker-marie-clemence-andriamonta-</ref>. Muri documentaire ye, umuziki ni ikintu cyingenzi kandi umuziki ukoreshwa nkibintu byerekana inkuru. Amenshi muri firime ayobowe na Clémence yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi mu iserukiramuco rya Cinéma du Réel<ref>https://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne_gen_cpersonne=49270.html</ref><ref>https://www.centrepompidou.fr/en/ressources/personne/SQY46yH</ref>. 

